<h4 id="a">A</h4>
<p>The title is named as data structure and algorithm, why this ? It means in a
program, you must have these two things.</p>

<ol>
  <li>data structure to describe your problem.</li>
  <li>algorithm to solve your problem by your solution.
    <ul>
      <li>this is trivial, but you need to realize this, during the array copy program,
the data structure is two array, target arrary and a blank array. Donâ€™t forgot
another data struct.</li>
      <li>pointer, yes it is trivial, but it is a data structure, we use an integer to
stands for this.</li>
      <li>After data structure well prepared, the algorithm begin.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Keep this in mind, data structure and algorithm, you need both of them in a
pgrogram.</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="a-1">A</h4>
<ol>
  <li>When I watch how Abdul Bari write a program, or implement an algorithm! Itâ€™s an
art.  He just do things in such an elegant and natural way.</li>
  <li>When he implement the BFS algorithm, he write the pseudo code step by step.
You feel like itâ€™s not difficult, itâ€™s natural, eazy, elegant beautiful.</li>
  <li>When he describe KMP algorithm, how he use the counter in pattern and target
string.</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="principal">Principal</h4>
<ol>
  <li>from simple to complex
    <ul>
      <li>suppose you need double layers for loops.</li>
      <li>first write the inside for-loop.</li>
      <li>then wirte the outside for-loop</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

